main.bio: I am a software developer with a passion for developing applications to solve real world problems. I am a full-stack web developer working primarily with React JS, Python Django-Rest, and SQL. My professional background is in project management within the Residential Real Estate field of the construction industry. I have a nact for problem solving and enjoy constantly learning new ways to solve problems.
